    "summary": {
      "value": "The twin ravens, messengers and spies of the gods."
    },
    "featureType": "projectfu.arcanum",
    "data": {
      "merge": "<h3>Winged Messengers</h3><p>You gain Resistance to <strong>air</strong> and <strong>bolt</strong> damage, and you are immune to <strong>dazed</strong>.</p><p>At the end of your turn during a conflict, you may choose one creature you can see. If you do, choose one option: the Game Master reveals one of that creature's <strong>Traits</strong>; <strong>or</strong>, the Game Master reveals that creature's Affinity to one damage type of your choice.</p>",
      "pulse": "",
      "dismiss": "<h3>Stormborn Twins</h3><p>Choose <strong>air</strong> or <strong>bolt</strong>. You deal 20 damage of the chosen type to one creature you can see; then, you deal 20 damage of the other type to one creature you can see (the same or a different one). Damage dealt by this effect ignores Resistances, and it ignores the Immunities of any creature you know <strong>two or more Traits</strong> of.</p><hr><p><strong>Enemy Suffers:</strong> @DMG[&step(20,30,40) air]{Air Damage}<br><strong>Enemy Suffers:</strong> @DMG[&step(20,30,40) bolt]{Bolt Damage}</p>",
      "domains": "knowledge, memory, storms"
    },
    "source": "FUBC34"
  },
